sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Detector as Regex Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Registry as Builtin Regex<br/>Registry (HashMap)
    participant Engine as Regex Engine<br/>(regex crate)

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 1: Text Content Detection

    Orchestrator->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>No Auth
    Note right of Orchestrator: Body: { content: "text...",<br/>  detector_params: {<br/>    regex: ["email", "ssn",<br/>      "credit-card",<br/>      "custom: ^\\d+$"]<br/>  }<br/>}

    alt Builtin Pattern (e.g. "email", "ssn", "credit-card")
        Detector->>Registry: Lookup builtin_regex[key]
        Registry-->>Detector: RegexDetection struct<br/>(compiled regex + metadata)
        Detector->>Engine: regex_match(pattern, text)
        Engine-->>Detector: Match positions
        Note right of Detector: detection_type: "pii"
    else Custom Pattern (arbitrary regex string)
        Detector->>Engine: Compile & match regex
        Engine-->>Detector: Match positions
        Note right of Detector: detection_type: "custom"
    end

    Detector-->>Orchestrator: HTTP 200 JSON Response<br/>[ { start, end, detection_type,<br/>  detection, text } ]

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 2: Health Check

    Orchestrator->>Detector: GET /health<br/>No Auth
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: HTTP 200 "healthy"
